## 4. TABS HORIZONTAIS — pill spring

```tsx
// UMA motion.div absoluta dentro do container
<motion.div
  className="pointer-events-none absolute rounded-[9999px]"
  animate={{ left: pillLeft, width: pillWidth }}
  transition={{ type: "spring", stiffness: 420, damping: 30, mass: 0.8 }}
  style={{ top: 6, bottom: 6, background: "#D7FF00" }}
/>
// Botões: relative z-10, bg: transparent, border-radius: rounded-[9999px]
// Container: bg #FFFFFF, rounded-[20px], padding: p-1.5
```

