## 5. MODAIS — 3 camadas, sempre

```tsx
<AnimatePresence>
  {open && (
    // Camada 1 — overlay
    <motion.div
      className="fixed inset-0 z-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4"
      initial={{ backgroundColor: "rgba(14,15,16,0)", backdropFilter: "blur(0px)" }}
      animate={{ backgroundColor: "rgba(14,15,16,0.70)", backdropFilter: "blur(12px)" }}
      exit={{ backgroundColor: "rgba(14,15,16,0)", backdropFilter: "blur(0px)" }}
      transition={{ duration: 0.25, ease: [0, 0, 0.2, 1] }}
      onClick={(e) => e.target === e.currentTarget && onClose()}
    >
      {/* Camada 2 — container */}
      <motion.div
        className="rounded-[20px] bg-white p-7"
        initial={{ scale: 0.88, y: 20, opacity: 0 }}
        animate={{ scale: 1, y: 0, opacity: 1 }}
        exit={{ scale: 0.92, y: 10, opacity: 0 }}
        transition={{ duration: 0.28, ease: [0, 0, 0.2, 1] }}
        onClick={(e) => e.stopPropagation()}
      >
        {/* Camada 3 — botão X */}
        <motion.button
          whileHover={{ rotate: 90, scale: 1.1 }}
          whileTap={{ rotate: 90, scale: 0.9 }}
          transition={{ duration: 0.15, ease: [0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1] }}
        >
          <X size={16} />
        </motion.button>
      </motion.div>
    </motion.div>
  )}
</AnimatePresence>
```

**`if (!open) return null` é PROIBIDO** — mata a animação de saída.
**Usar sempre `AnimatePresence` + `exit`.**

---

## 6. CARDS — stagger obrigatório

```tsx
// Toda lista de cards usa initial/animate com delay escalonado
<motion.div
  initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 16 }}
  animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}
  transition={{ duration: 0.3, ease: [0, 0, 0.2, 1], delay: Math.min(i * 0.06, 0.3) }}
  whileHover={{ y: -4 }}
  whileTap={{ scale: 0.98 }}
>
```

Cards NUNCA aparecem todos de uma vez.
Máximo de delay: 300ms (Math.min(i * 0.06, 0.3)).

---

## 7. TRANSIÇÕES DE PÁGINA

```tsx
// Em todo layout.tsx que envolve conteúdo de rota
<AnimatePresence mode="wait">
  <motion.div
    key={pathname}
    initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 12, filter: "blur(4px)" }}
    animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0, filter: "blur(0px)" }}
    exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -8, filter: "blur(3px)" }}
    transition={{ duration: 0.28, ease: [0, 0, 0.2, 1] }}
  >
    {children}
  </motion.div>
</AnimatePresence>
```

---

## 8. DROPDOWNS / MENUS FLUTUANTES

```tsx
<AnimatePresence>
  {open && (
    <motion.div
      initial={{ opacity: 0, y: -6, scale: 0.96 }}
      animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0, scale: 1 }}
      exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -6, scale: 0.96 }}
      transition={{ duration: 0.15, ease: [0, 0, 0.2, 1] }}
    >
```

**`{open && <div>}` sem AnimatePresence é PROIBIDO.**
**`shadow-lg` em dropdown é PROIBIDO** — usar borda `border-base-600` + bg `bg-surface-500`.

